lead_paragraph: John Tortorella had worried about Sunday's game, the first matinee for the Columbus all season. He didn't want the Washington Capitals to get off to a quick start.

headline.print_headline: Wennberg's Last-Minute Goal Gives Columbus 3-2 Win vs Caps
